# Backlog tasks

Use [.backlogs/_task.template.md](../../.backlogs/_task.template.md) and [INVEST](../../.notebook/00_references/invest.md).

## Task types

`feature` | `bugfix` | `refactor` | `deploy`

## Status gates

- `draft` — after `create-task-draft` → `{id}/draft/{id}.md`
- `ready` — INVEST complete → `{id}/ready/{id}.md`
- Design — `{id}/design/{id}.md` trước M+ code
- `in-progress` — develop → review → test → deploy (track on **ready** file)
- `done` — verification evidence + deploy (when applicable) + delivery report when handover required

## Skills

- New draft from intake: `create-task-draft`
- Harden / split: `planning-and-task-breakdown`
- Catalog alignment: `spec-driven-development`
- Design: `design-workflow`

See [.backlogs/README.md](../../.backlogs/README.md).
